gcc -I/usr/local/include -O2 -std=c99 -Wall -Werror -Wextra -Wuninitialized -Wcomments -Wwrite-strings -Wshadow -Wswitch-default -Wdeclaration-after-statement -Wcast-qual -Wcast-align -Wconversion -Wstrict-prototypes -Wmissing-prototypes -Wpointer-arith -Wbad-function-cast -Wswitch-enum

This will be used to compile .c files.

Examples...

gcc+glibc (glibc 2.20+) - the first 2 defines are required
gcc -D_DEFAULT_SOURCE -D_POSIX_SOURCE -I/usr/local/include -O2 -std=c99 -Wall -Werror -Wextra -Wuninitialized -Wcomments -Wwrite-strings -Wshadow -Wswitch-default -Wdeclaration-after-statement -Wcast-qual -Wcast-align -Wconversion -Wstrict-prototypes -Wmissing-prototypes -Wpointer-arith -Wbad-function-cast

gcc+glibc (< glibc 2.20) - the first 2 defines are required
gcc -D_BSD_SOURCE -D_POSIX_SOURCE -I/usr/local/include -O2 -std=c99 -Wall -Werror -Wextra -Wuninitialized -Wcomments -Wwrite-strings -Wshadow -Wswitch-default -Wdeclaration-after-statement -Wcast-qual -Wcast-align -Wconversion -Wstrict-prototypes -Wmissing-prototypes -Wpointer-arith -Wbad-function-cast

GCC 3.x
gcc -I/usr/local/include -O2 -std=c99 -Wall -Werror -Wuninitialized -Wcomments -Wwrite-strings -Wshadow -Wswitch-default -Wcast-qual -Wcast-align -Wstrict-prototypes -Wmissing-prototypes -Wpointer-arith -Wbad-function-cast

Other
gcc -I/usr/local/include -W -Wall -Werror -O2
